message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE. The paper discusses a deep learning based model for automatic question-answering, which falls under the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The model also involves finding similarity scores between pairs of questions and answers, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
